    &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;background&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;#23252e&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
